finger command is used to lookup information about an user.

adish007@ADISH007:~$ finger
Login     Name        Tty      Idle  Login Time   Office     Office Phone
adish007  ADISH.A.P  *:0             Dec 28 07:34 (:0)
adish007@ADISH007:~$ finger adish007
Login: adish007       			Name: ADISH.A.P
Directory: /home/adish007           	Shell: /bin/bash
On since Fri Dec 28 07:34 (IST) on :0 from :0 (messages off)
No mail.
No Plan.
